<L>__{exterior road near castle hackton day}
<A>__{roderick dismounts and gives the horse to one of the horse boys.}
<C>__{roderick}
<D>__{timmy, take the injured lad to see the doctor, and then bring the horse to doolan's farm, and tell him to break him in thoroughly. tell him it's for little patrick, and that i will be over to see him next week. horse boy yes, sir.}
<C>__{roderick}
<D>__{one more thing, and listen well, i don't want little patrick to know where the horse is being kept. it's going to be surprise for his birthday.}
